ORDER
This mattercame before the Court for hearing on June 11, 2025. The Father was present
along with his attorney, Dianne Davis, Esq., and the Mother's attorney, Barbie Agricola,
Esq., was present. The Mother was not present as she was in labor and presumably at a
hospital. The case was set for finalhearing on September 11, 2025.
Modificationof child support is held pending finalhearing. The Father is expected and
remains ordered to comply with the custody and visitation schedule set forth in the
finalorder.
DONE this 18thday of June, 2025.
/s/ KEVIN HALL
CIRCUIT JUDGE
